⚔️ PostgreSQL vs MongoDB (Deep Comparison)

🧱 1. Data Structure
| Feature   | PostgreSQL | MongoDB  |
| --------- | ---------- | -------- |
| Type      | Relational | Document |
| Structure | Tables     | JSON     |
| Schema    | Fixed      | Flexible |


🔗 2. Relationships
| Feature           | PostgreSQL | MongoDB   |
| ----------------- | ---------- | --------- |
| Joins             | ✅ Yes      | ❌ Limited |
| Foreign keys      | ✅ Yes      | ❌ No      |
| Complex relations | ✅ Strong   | ❌ Weak    |


3. Performance
| Case                | Winner     |
| ------------------- | ---------- |
| Complex queries     | PostgreSQL |
| Simple reads/writes | MongoDB    |
| Transactions        | PostgreSQL |

🔐 4. Data Integrity
| Feature     | PostgreSQL | MongoDB    |
| ----------- | ---------- | ---------- |
| ACID        | ✅ Strong   | ⚠️ Partial |
| Constraints | ✅ Yes      | ❌ Limited  |


